snippets.title: TelcoAutomation createBlueprint Sample
snippets.description: Creates a blueprint.

snippets.title: TelcoAutomation updateBlueprint Sample
snippets.description: Updates a blueprint.

snippets.title: TelcoAutomation getBlueprint Sample
snippets.description: Returns the requested blueprint.

snippets.title: TelcoAutomation deleteBlueprint Sample
snippets.description: Deletes a blueprint and all its revisions.

snippets.title: TelcoAutomation listBlueprints Sample
snippets.description: List all blueprints.

snippets.title: TelcoAutomation approveBlueprint Sample
snippets.description: Approves a blueprint and commits a new revision.

snippets.title: TelcoAutomation proposeBlueprint Sample
snippets.description: Proposes a blueprint for approval of changes.

snippets.title: TelcoAutomation rejectBlueprint Sample
snippets.description: Rejects a blueprint revision proposal and flips it back to Draft state.

snippets.title: TelcoAutomation listBlueprintRevisions Sample
snippets.description: List blueprint revisions of a given blueprint.

snippets.title: TelcoAutomation searchBlueprintRevisions Sample
snippets.description: Searches across blueprint revisions.

snippets.title: TelcoAutomation searchDeploymentRevisions Sample
snippets.description: Searches across deployment revisions.

snippets.title: TelcoAutomation discardBlueprintChanges Sample
snippets.description: Discards the changes in a blueprint and reverts the blueprint to the last approved blueprint revision. No changes take place if a blueprint does not have revisions.

snippets.title: TelcoAutomation listPublicBlueprints Sample
snippets.description: Lists the blueprints in TNA's public catalog. Default page size = 20, Max Page Size = 100.

snippets.title: TelcoAutomation getPublicBlueprint Sample
snippets.description: Returns the requested public blueprint.

snippets.title: TelcoAutomation createDeployment Sample
snippets.description: Creates a deployment.

snippets.description: Updates a deployment.

snippets.title: TelcoAutomation getDeployment Sample
snippets.description: Returns the requested deployment.

snippets.title: TelcoAutomation removeDeployment Sample
snippets.description: Removes the deployment by marking it as DELETING. Post which deployment and it's revisions gets deleted.

snippets.title: TelcoAutomation listDeployments Sample
snippets.description: List all deployments.

snippets.title: TelcoAutomation listDeploymentRevisions Sample
snippets.description: List deployment revisions of a given deployment.

snippets.title: TelcoAutomation computeDeploymentStatus Sample

snippets.title: TelcoAutomation rollbackDeployment Sample
snippets.description: Rollback the active deployment to the given past approved deployment revision.
